INSERT INTO WeighBridge (
	Docket,
	WB_Docket,
	Date,
	Rego,
	Supplier,
	Operations,
	Coupe,
	Harvestor,
	Gross,
	Tare,
	GMT,
	Grade,
	Length
)
VALUES (
	'{{IW_Validate_Form.formData.Docket}}',
	'{{iw_data_table.selectedRow.WB_Docket}}',
	'{{IW_Validate_Form.formData.Date}}',
	'{{IW_Validate_Form.formData.Rego}}',
	'{{IW_Validate_Form.formData.Supplier}}',
	'{{IW_Validate_Form.formData.Operations}}',
	'{{IW_Validate_Form.formData.Coupe}}',
	'{{IW_Validate_Form.formData.Harvestor}}',
	'{{IW_Validate_Form.formData.Gross}}',
	'{{IW_Validate_Form.formData.Tare}}',
	'{{IW_Validate_Form.formData.GMT}}',
	'{{IW_Validate_Form.formData.Grade}}',
	'{{IW_Validate_Form.formData.Length}}'
);
DELETE FROM Invalid_WeighBridge
  WHERE WB_Docket = {{iw_data_table.selectedRow.WB_Docket}};
